  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要建模客户和收货地址的关系。一个客户可以有多个地址，比如家里、公司这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那基数怎么定？是「一个客户对应一个或多个地址」还是允许零个？有些客户可能还没填地址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "1..one or more"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "从业务规则来看，注册时必须至少填一个地址，所以是1到多个。地址那边我觉得不需要反向查客户，单向关联就够了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "1..one or more",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以CUSTOMER通过「has」关系关联到DELIVERY-ADDRESS，基数1..one or more，单向。我先把实体名确定下来：CUSTOMER和DELIVERY-ADDRESS，中间用连字符。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "has",
        "1..one or more"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "DELIVERY-ADDRESS用连字符可以，强调这是配送专用地址，和普通地址区分开。关系名「has」没问题，简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已绘制：CUSTOMER实体通过「has」关系指向DELIVERY-ADDRESS，标注1..one or more。您看下布局有没有问题？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CUSTOMER",
        "DELIVERY-ADDRESS",
        "has",
        "1..one or more"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，基数标注我看错了，你写的是「1..*」？我们要的是明确写成「one or more」这种可读性强的形式，不是符号。",
      "elements_involved": [
